headline: Few Stocks Match Coca-Cola’s Dividend Stability
summary: The Coca-Cola Company (NYSE:KO) is among the best dividend stocks for a bear market. The company has paid a dividend since 1920 and has raised its annual payout for 63 consecutive years, a streak topped by only a few publicly traded companies. headline: Coca-Cola India Powers Ratha Yatra 2025 with Scaled Access, Cultural Integration, and Inclusive Growth
summary: Coca-Cola India is all set to mark its presence at one of the country's most iconic cultural celebrations - Ratha Yatra 2025 taking place in Puri, Odisha from 27th June to 5th July 2025. Building on its successful engagement at Maha Kumbh earlier this year, Coca-Cola will bring its refreshing beverage portfolio to the heart of the Ratha Yatra.
